item.description: Currently, I am a lecturer and an ARC DECRA Fellow (Australia Discovery Early Career Researcher Award) in School of Information Technology and Electrical Engineering (ITEE) in the University of Queensland (UQ). I am also an adjunct senior research fellow in Institute for Integrated and Intelligent Systems (IIIS) in Griffith University (GU). Previously, I worked as a lecture of computer science in School of Information and Communication Technology (ICT) in GU from July 2016 to January 2019.
